text: Taron David Egerton (born 10 November 1989) is a Welsh actor. His movie credits include Kingsman: The Secret Service (2014), Testament of Youth (2014), Legend (2015), Eddie the Eagle (2016), Kingsman: The Golden Circle (2017) and Rocketman (2019). For his role as Elton John in Rocketman, he won the Golden Globe Award for Best Actor â€“ Motion Picture Musical or Comedy. He has also appeared in the miniseries Watership Down (2018) and in the Apple TV+ film Tetris (2023). Egerton was born in Birkenhead, Merseyside. At a young age, he moved to Llanfairpwllgwyngyll on the Welsh island of Anglesey.
